No: Did you ever hear the like: But Zooks I fitted him once;
for I burnt a whole Stack of Hay down to the ground on that occasion,
and warm'd my self in spight of him.

Ay; but they say the best way of picking up Wenches is to speak
Bawdy to 'em. and the Truth is, I am a little shame-fac'd at present;
but I shall quickly come to't.

So, so—now they begin to fear me: I shall do well enough;
The Coat of the Tilbury's new-coin'd—Udshash 'tis as old as Tilbury
Camp, and that was in the same year with Noahs Flood.

The Country! Such another word and I'le renounce thee forever;
Prithee think no more on't: He'l be hang'd before he'l challenge
us.

